tell application "System Events" to tell application process "BetterDisplay"
    tell menu bar item 1 of menu bar 1
        click
        tell menu item "Manage Dummies" of menu 1
			click
			if menu item "Connect All Dummies" of menu 1 exists then
				click menu item "Connect All Dummies" of menu 1
			end if
			if menu item "Disconnect All Dummies" of menu 1 exists then
				click menu item "Disconnect All Dummies" of menu 1
			end if
		end tell
    end tell
end tell
